<p>Thursday 9 May</p>
<p>The expected barrage of Fritz's never came off, but we put one over on the left instead.  Perhaps that was what the original of the rumour said.</p>
<p>Started off for Caestre at about 6 p.m. on Tuesday evening, &ndash; about a dozen of us &ndash; three squads.</p>
